[
  {
    "start": 0.92,
    "end": 6.8,
    "text": "Hey guys, so today I want to talk a little bit about my machine here."
  },
  {
    "start": 6.8,
    "end": 12.1,
    "text": "You know all those years that I've been watching Star Trek, it's actually starting to pay off"
  },
  {
    "start": 12.1,
    "end": 17.88,
    "text": "you know with all the talk of lithium crystals and space modulators and all that stuff."
  },
  {
    "start": 17.88,
    "end": 19.28,
    "text": "I think I'm onto something here."
  },
  {
    "start": 19.28,
    "end": 24.76,
    "text": "So I took some basic household ingredients that you find laying around and I installed"
  },
  {
    "start": 24.76,
    "end": 34.12,
    "text": "them in just a certain sequence into my elliptical trainer here and I've achieved a near zero"
  },
  {
    "start": 34.12,
    "end": 36.16,
    "text": "gravity propulsion device."
  },
  {
    "start": 36.16,
    "end": 39.24,
    "text": "It's actually quite astounding."
  },
  {
    "start": 39.24,
    "end": 41.64,
    "text": "Let's have a look."
  },
  {
    "start": 41.64,
    "end": 43.68,
    "text": "So here is the basic command center."
  },
  {
    "start": 43.68,
    "end": 47.12,
    "text": "You've got your digital readout and you've got a button here."
  },
  {
    "start": 47.12,
    "end": 51.56,
    "text": "You know, oh look at that, the buttons, the LED has come up now."
  },
  {
    "start": 51.56,
    "end": 53.92,
    "text": "See I've actually armed this thing prematurely."
  },
  {
    "start": 53.92,
    "end": 54.72,
    "text": "I didn't want this thing."
  },
  {
    "start": 54.72,
    "end": 59.68,
    "text": "I was actually ready to start energizing but okay, well whatever, I've got it energized."
  },
  {
    "start": 59.68,
    "end": 66.68,
    "text": "And this is now, this looks like your, you know, basically your, it looks like, you know,"
  },
  {
    "start": 66.8,
    "end": 70.76,
    "text": "a knob where you would control the resistance on a normal elliptical trainer."
  },
  {
    "start": 70.76,
    "end": 73.92,
    "text": "Well now it's a neutron deflector."
  },
  {
    "start": 73.92,
    "end": 76.24,
    "text": "Quite ingenious actually."
  },
  {
    "start": 76.24,
    "end": 79.24,
    "text": "So we're going to try this thing out now."
  },
  {
    "start": 79.24,
    "end": 84.24,
    "text": "Okay, a little more adjusting on the, you know, the, the, the, the, the, the, the, the,"
  },
  {
    "start": 84.72,
    "end": 88.64,
    "text": "the neutron deflector here."
  },
  {
    "start": 88.64,
    "end": 94.6,
    "text": "Okay, I think, I think we should be ready now."
  },
  {
    "start": 94.6,
    "end": 96.8,
    "text": "Come on."
  },
  {
    "start": 96.8,
    "end": 101.32,
    "text": "Okay, I think."
  },
  {
    "start": 101.32,
    "end": 103.88,
    "text": "Should take off any minute."
  },
  {
    "start": 103.88,
    "end": 107.12,
    "text": "I can feel it."
  },
  {
    "start": 107.12,
    "end": 110.48,
    "text": "It's going to be good."
  },
  {
    "start": 110.48,
    "end": 112.72,
    "text": "Any minute."
  },
  {
    "start": 112.72,
    "end": 113.88,
    "text": "Any, oh."
  },
  {
    "start": 114.72,
    "end": 116.76,
    "text": "Here we go."
  },
  {
    "start": 116.76,
    "end": 117.84,
    "text": "We got it."
  },
  {
    "start": 117.84,
    "end": 118.96,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "start": 118.96,
    "end": 120.16,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "start": 120.16,
    "end": 121.16,
    "text": "Faster."
  },
  {
    "start": 121.16,
    "end": 124.16,
    "text": "Neutron deflector."
  },
  {
    "start": 144.72,
    "end": 159.08,
    "text": "Creating a neutron deflector-"
  },
  {
    "start": 159.08,
    "end": 161.78,
    "text": "Stupid neutron deflector!"
  },
  {
    "start": 161.78,
    "end": 166.76,
    "text": "Stupid proton deflector!"
  },
  {
    "start": 166.76,
    "end": 169.72,
    "text": "This is a late..."
  },
  {
    "start": 169.72,
    "end": 171.62,
    "text": "Science!"
  },
  {
    "start": 171.62,
    "end": 173.76,
    "text": "Science!"
  }
]